title: Bug 134040 - Row should not have page break property in Property Editor
OB: Page break can be set for a row in the Property Editor but cannot be saved.
EB: The row should not have the option to set a page break in the Property Editor.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Open the Property Editor.
2. Navigate to the row settings.
3. Look for the option to set a page break.

Expected result:
The option to set a page break should not be available for the row.

Actual result:
The option to set a page break is available for the row in the Property Editor but cannot be saved.
